{"tid":246235,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"美證交會傳將重新考慮批准4倍槓桿ETF上市 (05:39)","createTime":"2017-05-16T23:55:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-17T04:23:46.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ca0521dbbf072c0d777843c5ea5edb6e12ade804","tid":246235,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T23:55:02.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1GrZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=560f6873\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】據外媒引述消息人士稱，美國證交會(SEC)將會重新考慮批准首個4倍槓桿的交易所買賣基金(ETF)上市，意味着有關ETF的推出時間可能會有所延遲。<br />\n<br />\n於5月2日，SEC表示將批准ForceShares Daily 4X US Market Futures 正向和反向兩隻ETF上市。該兩隻ETF將追蹤標普500指數期貨的表現，為4倍槓桿型ETF。不過，有分析批評指，過高槓桿倍數的ETF可能會為投資者帶來風險，而市場亦可能難以承受其波動性過高。<br />\n<br />\n目前，美國的槓桿型基準指數ETF最多只有3倍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20170517/20170517053938fi.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Ffin%2F20170517%2F20170517053938fi.html&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1GrZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=c6446e52\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20170517/20170517053938fi.html</a>"},{"pid":"e9cfd9748d7f5e4bddaef961f29a97fd0ab4d3be","tid":246235,"uid":9526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T23:57:38.000Z","msg":"炒埋呢轉好走喇"},{"pid":"b4931c57a0e9dc54a93b3500d4f2d123bd1263c5","tid":246235,"uid":58913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T04:23:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>炒埋呢轉好走喇</blockquote><br />\n巴打睇淡美股嗎？"}]}